{"tid":971642,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"錯失咗一個上樓嘅機會","createTime":"2019-01-06T19:46:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-07T05:33:07.000Z","uid":212683,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"22e070c1d340b4b35404959c1a5431762d98f480","tid":971642,"uid":212683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T19:46:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LiEiyf4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLiEiyf4.png&h=6df2690a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係喊撚咗出嚟，開波前見皇蘇讓主隊一球球半，諗住屌，對手雖然係廢啫，但係對手話晒西甲老屎忽未降過班，加上又有主場優勢，應該都係一球上落㗎啫，點撚知皇蘇真係食得晒個盤，真係讓得起兩球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2019第一個發達機會咁就冇咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1183b7a9ecb9759ee0b466702d100d6fedc27461","tid":971642,"uid":226996,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T19:52:52.000Z","msg":"read"},{"pid":"c3a3f98b25e86105b98755b4db8e63617c60fd00","tid":971642,"uid":42153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T19:54:35.000Z","msg":"要上樓唔買盤啦直屌客<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8719257e614f41d708d5dadbf878a104717376bc","tid":971642,"uid":212683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3a3f98b25e86105b98755b4db8e63617c60fd00","tid":971642,"uid":42153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T19:54:35.000Z","msg":"要上樓唔買盤啦直屌客<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T19:56:40.000Z","msg":"你識唔識㗎，打主隊依啲咁嘅弱隊，單買客實好低水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55189fd3c32aa88da0a2d4744031b2b36e92b87a","tid":971642,"uid":186549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T20:57:05.000Z","msg":"我本身都諗住買波蛋0-2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cc2f6b03b67e759f76b4fb8cd875238204beba1","tid":971642,"uid":18654